refactor: simplify i18n to support only Chinese and English

Changes:
- Removed Japanese and Korean language support
- Simplified language detection logic (only Chinese vs English)
- Updated i18n module to only include zh and en prompts
- Updated index.js to only accept zh/en language parameters
- Updated documentation to reflect bilingual support only

Reason:
- Focus on most commonly used languages
- Reduce code complexity and maintenance burden
- Keep the codebase lean and maintainable

Supported languages:
- zh (中文)
- en (English)
